<a data-tip="p$t$ma-ke-chang" href="/people/ma-ke-chang">马克昌</a>，<strong title="会计" class="zu-question-my-bio">会计</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="96">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhou-ming-hao-16" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhou-ming-hao-16" class="zg-link" title="周明皓">周明皓</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-wei-54-56-27" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-wei-54-56-27" class="zg-link" title="李威">李威</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cartic" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cartic" class="zg-link" title="Cartic Cai">Cartic Cai</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


